<p><span class="anchor" id="p10"></span>٣ ٣/٣٣٢.<a href="#p10" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p11"></span>٤ المقنع مع الشرح الكبير والإنصاف ٥/٤٠٢.<a href="#p11" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p12"></span>٥ ليست في <span class="c1">"ح"</span>.<a href="#p12" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>